<br>
Seems like a really great idea to me. Anyone ever hear anything on this idea from VI? <p><b><font face="Tahoma" size="2" color="#0000FF">[55 Evoker] VortexTwin 
<Horizons></font></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugoramon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goramon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 10:59:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> Knock spell ?<br>
<br>
/boggle<br>
/shrug <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvortextwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>VortexTwin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:00:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> You know, a wizard form of lock pick. <p><b><font face="Tahoma" size="2" color="#0000FF">[55 Evoker] VortexTwin 
<Horizons></font></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ullaimpudu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>llaim Pudu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:02:46 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> I don't think that'll ever happen, Rogues need SOMETHING to keep em wanted! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><img src="http://members.home.net/wax32/images/llaim.jpg" align=left><font face=arial size=2>Adventurers on Fennin Ro:<BR>llaim Pudu, 55 Halfling Templar<br>locust Pudu, 53 Halfling Rake<br>Illnuu 30 Gnome Wizard<br><br><a href="http://frontpage.home.net/wax32/">The Pudu Brothers' Signpost</a></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugoramon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goramon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:02:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> I won't ask how you came up with &quot;Knock&quot; for a name, but nonetheless...<br>
<br>
I think it was tossed around a bit, and then tossed out.  It would take away something rogues are much needed for in the high end game, ie: that way we still need rogues =P <p><img src=http://divinusvirtus.freeservers.com/signatures/goramon.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usalladarahn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>salladarahn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:03:37 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> Knock is a D&amp;D spell, which when used opens locked doors.<br>
<br>
Would be pretty cool, but I can hear the rogues shapening their daggers already...... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:08:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> Yes, let's keep opening locks a rogue-exclusive skill, much like nukes ... no, wait ...<br>
<br>
Much like direct damage ... no ...<br>
<br>
Well, like ports ... damn it ...<br>
<br>
Like translocates are a wizard exclusive.<br>
<br>
I forgot my point. And I've already asked for a Knock spell on the Developer's Corner. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umcdermit.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mcdermit</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:16:18 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.home.com/zwobu/z.jpeg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> Roleplayers that don't know what Knock is? Gary Gygax must be spinning in his grave! (Hehe, he's not really dead, is he?)<br>
<br>
It does frustrate me quite a bit that I can manipulate time and space to teleport myself and others all over the globe, but that there's no way for me to get through an ordinary locked door. Fade should take me through doors. Bolt spells should blast doors open. We should have some Knock or Telekinesis spell to nudge the lock open.<br>
<br>
Even if Rogues are made to share lockpicking duties with Wizards, they'll still be wanted for their damage output ;) <p><center>Zwobu &lt;Trade Foundation&gt; Innoruuk<br><i>"Zwobu [will be] the First against the Wall when the REVOLUTION COMES" -- Dmitry the Wizzy</i></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utorcerarcana.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Torcer Arcana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 11:42:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1>      I don't want to open any locked doors unless I can blow them apart with my nukes.  I guess if we got &quot;knock&quot; then we would need to get &quot;Wizard Lock&quot; too.  Now tell me it wouldn't be fun to Wizard Lock that door to the surface in Blackburrow and watch the pile of bodies stack as the newbies tried to avoid the inevitable train.  j/k. <p>Torcer Arcana<Br>Level 55 Wizard<Br>The Nameless</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 12:23:13 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> Isn't that already there, Torcer? I think the spell is called &quot;LD Barbarian.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uteaenea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teaenea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 12:57:37 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> The ironic thing is, the rogues I know HATE have to be doormen.  Heh, if they only had to face the port issue. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/useiryueq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SeiryuEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 12:57:49 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://seiryu.freewebspace.com/seiryu.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> When the possibility of familiars being pets arose a lot of people said: we are not mages/necros! Wizards = no pets.<br>
<br>
Now a spell to pick lock doors? I have to disagree, this is a skill reserved for rogues. As a wizard I prefer to specialize in pure offensive magic. No buff, no pet, no pick lock spell.<br>
<br>
Seiryu <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umadleon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Madleon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 1:03:30 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.packetlost.com/ho/im/headache.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: - Knock - </span><hr size=1> I do agree that our shadowstep/yonder spells are bascially useless outside of PvP and that these SHOULD be an option for us to get through locked doors.  <p><center><a href="http://www.packetlost.com"><img src="http://www.packetlost.com/ho/eq/xaxsig.jpg"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6270.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6237.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6273.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6273.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6273.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6273.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to sto